name: STRANGECREATURES 01
description:
Time to get back to my roots. 

My formative years as a youth were in the early to mid-90s when rap, grunge, and punk music dominated the airwaves and the space between my ear holes. My walls were collaged with jewel case cover art from my favorite bands and it’s around that time that I started drawing these strange creatures. 

As my work evolved over the years, the strange creatures were something I always came back to. A comfortable default. So in this new space for me as an artist, I think it’s time to take a deeper dive into the strange creatures.

STRANGECREATURES 01 is a nostalgic callback to that simpler time for me. Let the punk wave wash over you.

1620x2880
